	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />There are two codes, one for BRAM-&gt;cart, and for cart-&gt;BRAM; cart-&gt;BRAM's code is "10005XXXXXXXX1".

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

