	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Thanks.  One more follow-up question.  How do you initiate the cart -&gt; BRAM transfer?  I presume that the write BRAM command won't automatically do this.  Do you need to load the game and then initiate a save, or is merely loading the game from dumper memory sufficient to pull the cart memory into BRAM?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


